thumb180\/61e7f4aaly1gdddv32wsxj21010u010f.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/c21128ec52dc05dd_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#导演佐佐部清去世#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#导演佐佐部清去世# 据日媒，导演佐佐部清于3月31日去世，享年62岁。佐佐部清曾执导过《朝阳又升》《半告白》《七夕之夏》《丈夫得了抑郁症》等片，与西田敏行、渡边谦、田中丽奈、宫崎葵、堺雅人等都有过合作。据悉，佐佐部清执导的新片《拔河祭之恋》，本计划在今年秋天上映。[蜡烛] ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/0f95513ec56f1e0d_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/0f95513ec56f1e0d_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx1.sinaimg.cn\/crop.0.58.825.458\/67dd74e0gy1gddggad549j20mx0g011g.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/0f95513ec56f1e0d_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">张国荣<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">张国荣经典歌曲。\n\n又是一年四月一，一生未见，一世怀念。[心]\n\n《共同渡过+风继续吹+沉默是金+当年情+倩女幽魂+童年时+似水流年+但愿人长久+春夏秋冬+有心人+有谁共鸣+热情的沙漠+追+Monica+月亮代表我的心》\n\n视频1个小时，建议先马后看。#十七周年继续宠爱张国荣#  http:\/\/t.cn\/A6ZoRiAS ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/57729e15fb01b0ef_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/57729e15fb01b0ef_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/73977c05ly1gddljcmzcnj211x1kwahv.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/57729e15fb01b0ef_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_tx